data.text:
HIGH SCHOOL

Was named First Team All-State, All-Region, All-District, and All-Conference after his junior season ... Was named All-District and All-Conference as a sophomore ... Due to a US Soccer rule, that took effect in 2012, was unable to compete for his high school squad due to his playing with the Academy squad ... He plays for the NPL U-18 squad, and was the leading scorer for his Academy U-17 squad the year before, a team that was a state semifinalist, and helped the U-16 squad to a regional runner-up a year earlier.
